    "response": "Dear soul,  the paths of Yoga—Karma, Bhakti, Jnana, and Raja—all lead to union with the Divine.  The best path is the one that resonates most deeply with your heart.\n\nAs I teach in Bhagavad Gita 18.46: **योगः कर्मसु कौशलम्** (*yogaḥ karmasu kauśalam*) - Yoga is skill in action.\n\nFind your path through dedicated practice and self-reflection. May you find your way. 🕉️\n",
